Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:03.42,shangzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,(Nadua )阿娜ENDORA大陆的幻之种族，曾经缔造了非常高的文明你们两位都清醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:11.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,男生就是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不断碰撞不断交锋最终相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,男人之间就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:27.58,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:32.51,geci,,0,0,0,,那正在微笑的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:43.10,geci,,0,0,0,,用足以扼杀孤独的力量  紧紧拥抱我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:51.40,geci,,0,0,0,,被束缚的Limit  解放它回归本始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:53.48,geci,,0,0,0,,纵燃燃殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:01:03.79,geci,,0,0,0,,也要在这渲染了艳丽的夜之尽头翩然起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.66,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:17.43,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:24.27,geci,,0,0,0,,在这夜之尽头  翩然起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.31,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:36.23,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.61,geci,,0,0,0,,飞扬而上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:44.91,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还远远不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:07.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王都周边的领主们果然大多数都是站在德尔扎因那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:14.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  别说理解我们的志向了他们甚至可以说几乎都是反革命军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能成为伙伴的话战力也将得到扩充
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:23.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但感觉上我们和他们在相互理解的前一步还存在着问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:29.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里往北的领主  受到德尔扎因庇护的很少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的  我们或多或少也能得到一些领主的赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:37.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  那些曾反抗过王的人都被流放到北方边境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家对于受到这种待遇一定觉得不满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:45.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此  但我们尚未掌握到王国军的详细情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,八万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:46.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王国军士兵数大约近八万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  比我们预想的还多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:03:00.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就算我们现在起义  也是摆明了要吃败仗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话我不想有任何人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让这次革命建立在牺牲的基础上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥  话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但要招募到超过王国军的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是要花多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,关键就在这里  果然还是希望能得到他们帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,祖乌族  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:22.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉拢祖乌族成为伙伴  你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为真的可以与他们顺利沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟祖乌族有过接触吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们作为德尔扎因的护卫听从他的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:41.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…不  是我在城外袭击我的那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙强得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  那家伙感觉好想不是光凭语言就能相互沟通理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你有尝试过去跟他交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再碰面的话试着跟他交流一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在王的暴政下饱受折磨的祖乌族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也许会赞同我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果成功的话  他们定能成为可靠的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,露易丝  到时候就拜托你为我们牵线搭桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:17.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,找个地方和他们认真的谈一场  希望他们能够对我们的想法产生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想将他们当作是单纯的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎觉得听不太懂你们话的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你们快点带我去巴比伦就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:33.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,结果所谓革命就是打倒德尔扎因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,国王大人大概现在正朝巴比伦进发哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王前往巴比伦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个来吧  我帮你们处理伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:53.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥他真的打算拉拢祖乌作为伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的确是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  真的能够成为伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:05.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果真可行的话就不用依靠这家伙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:09.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着革命军去往巴比伦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这个惹人厌的家伙怎样也不关我事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一看到这家伙的脸就气不打一处来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌到不想和他一同呼吸同一片空气的地步真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  哪里痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你们打得那么热火朝天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  我会好好帮你们处理伤ロ的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:34.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来  到里面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  原来和这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么了  快点进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:49.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们再继续站着  小心被ENDORA蚊咬到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:53.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,蚊子不就只是普通的蚊子而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是小事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:06:00.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被ENDORA蚊子咬到的话全  身的血都会被它吸干变成干尸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是吸血鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血…鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先去拿药过来你们就在里面等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  祖乌族指的就是那个凶暴的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的样子也不寻常到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:23.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:24.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又在吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥真的打算拉拢祖乌族当同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那些凶暴的家伙真的能跟他们沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:54.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为人与人并非平等  但却不能剥夺任何人的自由生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是迪米特里奥一直挂在嘴边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,祖乌族之所以会变得凶暴  这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:07.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,ENDORA人是名为阿娜杜亚的种族和人类生下的混血人种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:11.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而阿娜杜亚人弓动物之间所诞生的则是祖乌族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在很久很久以前  两个种族之间本没有纷争和平共存着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但后来ENDORA人却开始迫害祖乌族人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,厉代的王是这么考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通过奴役比自己地位低下的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,藉以实现统一ENDORA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直遭受迫害的祖乌族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有想过自己有一天能够和ENDORA人处在平等的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体里也流着的血有一半是祖乌族的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了一跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,光从外表看不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,祖乌族人大多神色可怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还有不善言辞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会让人感到害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的那个对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了来疗伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:00.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一位先来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:01.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我先来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:03.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都说是我先了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆两个人一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦把脸伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐露易丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥有跟祖乌族交流过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:16.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥的家族是贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且代代都是领主可谓一大名门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:25.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直过着富裕的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就那样醉生梦死地过下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以活得更加轻松些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经有一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是祖乌族的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我我把这些给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个宅邸的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪  迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫卢西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个胆小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,送到这里  你应该可以自己一个人回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了  迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥  还能再见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你想要见我的话  就这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥  你有化宝具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:28.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:30.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我才这么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有化宝具的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟化宝具什么的没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:35.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好好磨练本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:41.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我再怎么磨炼  没有化宝具的话一样无法变强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:42.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你身怀勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:59.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你不也是冲得比我更早吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,身手的话  只要锻练就会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  勇气是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  去吃些美食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:18.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多该回去了吧  家人会担心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  下个月我就15岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是堂堂成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呵  成年人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂还不快给我站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要休息到什么时候你这废物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你算老几跟你无关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个人  你的行为让人无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:47.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:53.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这臭小子  区区祖乌族居然对人用化宝具搞清楚你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:56.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:58.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢...西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:21.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  卢西奥全是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:32.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能够遇见你真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢西奥  我会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:04.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伤ロ暂时是处理好了 但他们还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不管没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又吵架了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,男人就是不断碰撞不断交锋最终相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然男人都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么革命  什么打倒国王真是超麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有什么能让我更快回去的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:39.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥那家伙真的认为能够拉拢祖乌族成为同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:43.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  明天再问一下那个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,革命什么的无所谓  只要能干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙随他去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:02.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔乔亚先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:05.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能打扰一下你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:13.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天你说预见到了未来  就不能看得更清楚些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再看一次的话说不定就能明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:25.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  你看那里好像有什么东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔乔亚先生  去把它拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我预见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:58.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能找到ENDORA蓝鸟你就能回到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:15:59.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉鸟在那个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:02.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,ENDORA蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有那种鸟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报复一下  谁叫他想害我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不遇上危险就无法预见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但说实话  我自己也不知道在什么情况下能够预见未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据报告  这片区域里存在着革命军的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王子和那个少年好像就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳茨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便收拾他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:48.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小子怎么办  干掉也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,随你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别对王子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:01.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:07.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我去会会他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪呐  完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,又见面了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在城堡那里碰到的祖乌族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你能记住本爷  真让人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  王子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:17:59.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个狂妄自大的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这我并不讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好强  这样下去的话会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:09.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论他怎么样  明明都和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:13.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的话根本无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要管那家伙的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:37.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要受到你的帮助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别烦了  赶紧站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:44.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:47.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是  明明只会扯后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在首要目标是打倒那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王子  虽说上头是叫我把你带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就带着你的尸体回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是伊格纳茨的首领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我的名字是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,名字什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,反正伊格纳茨会被埋葬于此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你得逞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那我就先把你给收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,化宝具居然进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好机会  艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他了…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被德尔扎因那样颐指气使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不觉得悲哀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:36.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,区区革命军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格对我的生存方式说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我等将力量借于强者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,并以此获取报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:44.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这种行为叫做将灵魂出卖给了权力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:13.42,geci,,0,0,0,,兜兜转转   迂迂回回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:21.51,geci,,0,0,0,,时至今日的种种  成就了今天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:28.35,geci,,0,0,0,,go my way    go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:48.62,geci,,0,0,0,,世界轮回   将从未见过的未来映照于青空之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:57.34,geci,,0,0,0,,超越过去超越自我
